data.description: So many valuable improvements have been made on this home: vinyl double hung windows, flooring, hardwood trim, kitchen cabinets, bathroom updates. Main floor primary bedroom has attached 3/4 bath and walk-in closet. Upper level has its own entrance with a kitchen, family room, bedroom, and 3/4 bath. Large lot with detached cemented pole-style garage and large carport. Sellers will be leaving everything that is currently on the property, including the garage contents. Property is being sold "As Is".
